#

Spicy Garlic Butter Shrimp

20 min
$15
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeLow-Carb

Cuisine:

AmericanSeafood

Course:

Main CourseDinner

Tags:

Quick MealSeafoodSpicy

Description

Succulent shrimp sautéed in a spicy garlic butter sauce, perfect for a quick and flavorful meal!

Ingredients

  • shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 pound
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • garlic (minced): 4 cloves
  • red pepper flakes: 1 teaspoon
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • fresh parsley (chopped): 2 tablespoons
